name: Dark Acamar
description:
Click to play - better with headphones.

With this work we wanted to mix analog and digital sounds with generative art.
The artwork and the music respond to each other to amplify the oppressive atmosphere which gives this feeling of being crushed.

How to stand up while facing oppression... that's the question that lead us to this artwork.

Song by Antoine & Noctambul.
Generative art by Noctambul.
